snippet.title: Mealmates
snippet.description:
🎮 Get Mealmates on Steam https://tinyurl.com/y6o8hhrd
🎮 Get Mealmates Itch.io https://magicdweedoo.itch.io/mealmates
🎵 Get Soundtrack on Bandcamp https://dweedes.bandcamp.com/album/mealmates-ost
🎵 Listen to Soundtrack on Spotifty https://tinyurl.com/y3vzrrfn
👕 L00t https://wetgamin.bigcartel.com

Get your friends together or play by yourself. It's a minigame mayhem! Whoever produces the most delicious Mealmate will win eternal glory.

Dress up your Mealmate in the latest fashions, cook gastronomical delights, explore the mysterious town and more in the greatest multimedia experience of the year.
